<i>It is the key essence of roller skates.</i>

66
00:04:37,210 --> 00:04:42,682
{\an8}Roller skates were the reason
for Kis-My-Ft2's formation.

67
00:04:42,749 --> 00:04:44,951
{\an8}TAKASHI NIKAIDO

68
