80
00:05:54,454 --> 00:05:56,289
<i>It's time to speak in Mandarin.</i>

81
00:05:57,590 --> 00:06:01,861
<i>We are Kis-My-Ft2!</i>

82
00:06:02,495 --> 00:06:04,664
<i>You are pretty.</i>

83
00:06:08,568 --> 00:06:10,136
I was so nervous.

84
00:06:10,203 --> 00:06:11,738
You did great.

85
00:06:12,205 --> 00:06:16,275
<i>We ask the local media
what they think of Kisumai.</i>

86
